data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! 🌳 Tucked away on a generous half-acre lot, this charming older house has been meticulously updated to suit the modern homeowner's desires. With a perfect blend of classic character and contemporary amenities, this home offers the best of both worlds. Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area is adorned with beautiful laminate floors, while large windows flood the space with natural light. The kitchen is a chef's paradise, boasting top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, quarts countertops, and ample storage space.Prepare delicious meals while enjoying the view of your expansive backyard through the window.But the real gem of this property lies outside. The half-acre lot provides endless possibilities for outdoor enthusiasts. Imagine hosting summer barbecues on the spacious patio, lounging under the shade of mature trees, or starting your own garden to cultivate your green thumb.
Conveniently located close to the Ohio river, this home offers a peaceful retreat while still being within close proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, and more.
Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a beautifully updated older home on a generous half-acre lot. Embrace the charm of the past with the comfort of modern living. Schedule a tour today and make this your forever home!
